name: Knowledge.Jokes.Dad jokes.Why do you never see

speech: A furniture store keeps calling me. All I wanted was one night stand. I used to work in a shoe recycling shop. It was sole destroying. Did I tell you the time I fell in love during a backflip? I was heels over head. My wife is really mad at the fact that I have no sense of direction. So I packed up my stuff and right. Did you hear about the restaurant on the moon? Great food, no atmosphere. When does a joke become a dad joke? When it becomes apparent! What do you call a fake noodle? An Impasta.
Because they're so good at it.
